            <title>[LU-18779] lnetctl SIGSEGV in lnetctl.c getopt_internal()</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-18779</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Program received signal SIGSEGV, Segmentation fault. 0x0000fffff7d55b04 in _getopt_internal_r () from /lib64/libc.so.6 #0 &#160;0x0000fffff7d55b04 in _getopt_internal_r () from /lib64/libc.so.6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#1 &#160;0x0000fffff7d56094 in _getopt_internal () from /lib64/libc.so.6&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#2 &#160;0x00000000004291b0 in jt_show_net (argc=2, argv=0xffffffffdd28) at lnetctl.c:3717&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#3 &#160;0x0000fffff7f87524 in cfs_parser_execarg (cmds=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;, argv=0xffffffffdd28, argc=2) at util/parser.c:174&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#4 &#160;cfs_parser (argc=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;, argv=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;, cmds=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;) at util/parser.c:157&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#5 &#160;0x000000000042bb28 in jt_net (argc=3, argv=0xffffffffdd20) at lnetctl.c:3977&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#6 &#160;0x0000fffff7f870d8 in execute_line (line=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;) at util/parser.c:370&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#7 &#160;0x0000fffff7f876e0 in cfs_parser_commands (cmds=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;) at util/parser.c:483&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#8 &#160;cfs_parser (argc=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;, argv=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;, cmds=&amp;lt;optimized out&amp;gt;) at util/parser.c:159&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;#9 &#160;0x0000000000443630 in main (argc=1, argv=0xffffffffef48) at lnetctl.c:5925&lt;/p&gt;</description>
